    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title">登入失敗</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>您的帳號狀態有異常，請來信詢問<a href="mailto:paipaigo001@@gmail.com">客服</a>。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="loginModal2" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="loginFailureModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title">登入失敗</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>Email地址或密碼不正確，請檢查您的登入資訊並再試一次。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

